REMARK   0 Minimal multi-model structure (NMR-style).
REMARK   0 Bug: hydrogen placement only wrote to model 0; second model lacked H
REMARK   0      on repeated calls (not idempotent). Fixed 2026-04-08.
MODEL        1
ATOM      1  N   ALA A   1       1.000   1.000   1.000  1.00  0.00           N
ATOM      2  CA  ALA A   1       2.000   1.000   1.000  1.00  0.00           C
ATOM      3  C   ALA A   1       3.000   1.000   1.000  1.00  0.00           C
ATOM      4  O   ALA A   1       3.000   2.000   1.000  1.00  0.00           O
ATOM      5  N   GLY A   2       4.000   1.000   1.000  1.00  0.00           N
ATOM      6  CA  GLY A   2       5.000   1.000   1.000  1.00  0.00           C
ATOM      7  C   GLY A   2       6.000   1.000   1.000  1.00  0.00           C
ATOM      8  O   GLY A   2       6.000   2.000   1.000  1.00  0.00           O
ENDMDL
MODEL        2
ATOM      1  N   ALA A   1       1.100   1.100   1.100  1.00  0.00           N
ATOM      2  CA  ALA A   1       2.100   1.100   1.100  1.00  0.00           C
ATOM      3  C   ALA A   1       3.100   1.100   1.100  1.00  0.00           C
ATOM      4  O   ALA A   1       3.100   2.100   1.100  1.00  0.00           O
ATOM      5  N   GLY A   2       4.100   1.100   1.100  1.00  0.00           N
ATOM      6  CA  GLY A   2       5.100   1.100   1.100  1.00  0.00           C
ATOM      7  C   GLY A   2       6.100   1.100   1.100  1.00  0.00           C
ATOM      8  O   GLY A   2       6.100   2.100   1.100  1.00  0.00           O
ENDMDL
END
